divs: sighting detailsfriday evening i spotted a fireball in the western\northwestern sky of land o lakes, fl. it was a very large sized fireball kinda falling\sailing and then vanished in the air. it was a bright orange ball that seemed to be flaming, but not necessarily on fire. looked more like the "vapor"\fumes of a fire. i guess like looking at the top portion of flames burning in a grill or gas stove. if that makes any sense. i decided to post this sighting to hopefully get others in the area to submit their own sightings in the area.
